  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: a1c44d26bee7f894782729c6bcff2b73, type: 3}
  m_Name: Chives Conversation 1
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  SpeakerName: Yukio
  paragraphs:
  - ' really? you just let your talents go to waste sometimes.'
  - what? i was trying something new okay.
  - "yeah well, don\u2019t\u201D \u201Cgod i want to have a nap now"
  - not before you tell me about your night, did you do what i asked
  - "fine.\u201Dyawns* \u201Cbut yes of course i did because i\u2019m great at what
    i do\u201D \u201Ci got in contact with Kenji - the detective you remember?"
  - of course
  - "right, well this guy was really strange but he agreed without hesitation\u201D
    \u201Cat this point so many detectives have turned us down this guy could be
    anyone and i\u2019d hire him"
  - "thank god, and i agree, i\u2019ve waited too long already. i miss him."
  - "its okay yukio, i\u2019m always here"
  - ...
  - except for right now, i got things (and the girl from last night) to do
  - right, have fun with that
  - bye! and next time PLEASE feed me something less boring
